{"id":661993,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":10,"day":19}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"108","ytitle":"","mtitle":"悼谭震林同志","ftitle":"","authors":["刘瑞龙"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘瑞龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谭老遽长逝，战友泪沾襟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕生为民仆，党节骨铮铮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立身秉刚直，行事世所钦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斥逆针锋对，无畏献忠诚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严整治军旅，智断胜敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战后掌农政，深入探索勤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热情扶后进，砥砺感知音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻苦学马列，勇于自我评。"}]}